string.name: how_rtgs_work
string.u: How RTGS work on Direct App

string.name: how_to_add_rtgs_amount
string.u: How to add money into RTGS account

resources.string: To be paid 2 hour before delivery T&C*

How to use RTGS Bal on Direct App :

  1. Add balance to RTGS account via Netbanking/Bank in the Beneficiary detail mentioned on the RTGS Detail page
  2. While Placing order choose RTGS Bal as preferred Payment option
  3. On delivery of the order, authorize the delivery boy to deduct the amount from your RTGS account using OTP
  4. Once the order is delivered the amount will be deducted from your RTGS Bal and order payment will be processed

RTGS Bal update using Net banking :

  • Go to your bank’s official website
  • Login to the net banking account
  • Once you log in, add the details of the beneficiary mentioned in the RTGS details screen of the app
  • Once the details of the beneficiary are added, go to the option of RTGS transactions
  • Enter the details of the beneficiary and the payment to be processed to make the transactions
  • Submit the application and the funds will be transferred to the beneficiary

Alternatively, you can transfer money through RTGS directly from the bank manually by filling form.
